{"tid":2233579,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"家長力撐教材沒問題","createTime":"2020-10-07T08:39:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T08:45:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"33d250effee4074cd3fa48dd0871092d0022676d","tid":2233579,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T08:39:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201007/526FRXLIEZB6ZE7HF764DW6ONA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201007%2F526FRXLIEZB6ZE7HF764DW6ONA%2F&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmaP8PJJZD286lWcuKEclkJo%3D&h=c0627d36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201007%2F526FRXLIEZB6ZE7HF764DW6ONA%2F&h=c9d32838\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201007/526FRXLIEZB6ZE7HF764DW6ONA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n家長力撐教材沒問題<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】教育局指九龍塘宣道小學一名教師在教材中散播「港獨」訊息，並取消他的註冊資格。該校家長紛紛力撐涉事的教師，認為教材內容沒有問題，更形容該教師關心學生，是位好老師，對今次事件感到傷心。亦有家長不滿當局處分過於嚴苛，批評「有恐嚇成份」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：林鄭辣手清算 嘲前朝避難  學者轟𢱑爛面殺雞儆猴<br />\n<br />\n宣道小學校董會則發聲明指，該名遭取消註冊的教師已離職，因涉及個人私隱，不便回應其他事情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3aRyur74C9MifkfEoysbSWtbjvc=/640x361/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YMMVZYKPYZBTPDKCQ24TCW2OTE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3aRyur74C9MifkfEoysbSWtbjvc%3D%2F640x361%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYMMVZYKPYZBTPDKCQ24TCW2OTE.jpg&h=c78770a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■家長周先生認為從工作紙「睇唔到所謂嘅陰謀」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1nFdlInqH32VbuARIa-6hZiqiLk=/640x481/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/35YZX744Y5EWXE6H2FZNSMLKYE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1nFdlInqH32VbuARIa-6hZiqiLk%3D%2F640x481%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F35YZX744Y5EWXE6H2FZNSMLKYE.jpg&h=4158eb28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■家長林先生認為學校應是讓學生學習、討論的場地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n痛惜關心學生「好老師」<br />\n<br />\n子女分別就讀該校小二、小三的周先生表示，曾經看過相關教材工作紙，認為內容沒有問題，沒有「要港獨」的前設，「睇唔到所謂嘅陰謀。」周又稱，涉事的老師曾教導其子，形容他有資歷、有耐性，是位「好老師」、「好關心學生」。對該老師被取消註冊感到可惜、遺憾、傷心。更擔心該校教師之後會自我審查。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：副秘粵劇腔朗誦罪狀<br />\n<br />\n同樣認識涉事教師的小六學生家長劉先生則向記者讚賞他「很用心教小朋友」。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n劉指政府可能擔心學生被「整歪思想」，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n小一學生家長黃太則對事件感到愕然，質疑現時「政府做好多嘢都令我哋意想不到」。對於校長及其他教師同樣受到譴責及收警告信，她認為很無辜，坦言感到心痛，又憂慮事件令學校教師自我審查。"},{"pid":"757aa38f1581f0ff8b1bc32ddc1a846c592ce6df","tid":2233579,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T08:45:24.000Z","msg":"黨話有問題呀，黨先係香港政府嘅老細<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images1.epochhk.com/pictures/155334/photo6266791850111248864@1200x1200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages1.epochhk.com%2Fpictures%2F155334%2Fphoto6266791850111248864%401200x1200.jpg&h=bb385315&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}